Once you find the item you decide to buy, you can add it to your personal virtual basket by clicking on the button "Add to Cart" next to each item. You repeat the procedure for all items that you want to buy. At the top of the website, you can keep track contents of the basket. By clicking on the shopping cart you will see a button for the Checkout. Enter all necessary information for delivery, choose a delivery and payment method, and familiarize yourself with the terms and conditions . If you decide to buy, by clicking on the "order with a payment obligation" button, confirm your decision and submit your order. Now your order is placed. You will be notified by e-mail about all the following steps.

Yes, the purchade made with us is completely safe.

When you submit your order, you also provide us with your personal information. We use this information only for delivery, notification of the order and fulfillment of our legal obligations. On the pages where personal data is transmitted, we use an encrypted link, so malicious people or programs can not intercept data transmitted between a site and a visitor.

We use only payment methods that do not provide us with confidential information about your bank accounts. In case of payment to a bank account, you provide all the information to the bank, which then makes a payment to our bank account. PayPal payments are made through the PayPal system, the same applies to payment with payment cards.

For protection of personal data, is also responsible user itself, by using appropriate software (antivirus) protection.

Registration is NOT required to make a purchase.

On checkout select option "buy without registration". After placing products you like in cart, enter the information we need to delivery, select payment and shipping option and place an order. If you decide to register, you can do this whenever you place an order by selecting the "Registration" option. This makes it easier for you to re-order and in the future provides some benefits. If you change your mind, you can erase your account at any time in accordance with the law.
